Man on the Moon;;79;;64;;R;;Jim Carrey stars as the late Andy Kaufman, who was considered one of the most innovative, eccentric and enigmatic performers of his time. A master at manipulating audiences, Kaufman could generate belly laughs, stony silence, tears or brawls. Whether inviting the audience out for milk and cookies or challenging women to inter-gender wrestling matches, he specialized in creating performances so real that even his close friends were never sure where the truth lay.;;Biography;;Milos Forman;;1999;;Jim Carrey,J. Alan Thomas,Bob Zmuda,Max Alexander,Peter Bonerz,Bobby Boriello,Brent Briscoe,Randall Carver,Jeff Conaway,Danny DeVito,Tom Dreesen,Budd Friedman,Paul Giamatti,Marilu Henner,Judd Hirsch,Angela Jones,Carol Kane,Jerry Lawler,David Letterman,Christopher Lloyd;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1093579-man_on_the_moon